  "keyFeatures": [
    "Browser-based interface for Active Directory penetration testing — no CLI juggling required",
    "Persistent SQLite credential store with deduplication and auto-population of authenticated scan dropdowns",
    "Playwright-powered web screenshots with technology detection, value scoring, and VPN-transparent rendering",
    "Layer 2 attack tools (Responder, mitm6, ASRepCatcher) with live output streaming and start/stop controls",
    "Full AD attack chain: BloodHound, Kerberoast, AS-REP Roasting, ADCS (ESC1–ESC8+), GMSA, Pre2K, Delegation, and more",
    "Vulnerability checks: PrintNightmare, SMBGhost, EternalBlue, noPAC, Zerologon, Coerce, MasterBaiter payloads",
    "Kerberos ccache support with automatic clock sync and ccache-based authenticated scans",
    "Hash Calculator: derive NTLM, AES-128, and AES-256 Kerberos keys from plaintext passwords using impacket"
  ],
